items.summary:
Positive: 
-Dark themed story, lovecraftian horror style, well written;
- Good character design;
- Nice soundtrack;
- Fair pity on the gatcha and easilly obtainable pull currency;
- Faction system that gives very different playstiles for different color themed decks. 

Negative:
- Bad translation. Like really bad, some skills and effects have like 2-3 different word for the same thing (i'm looking at you ultra faction gimmicks). This is specially bad because the game is complex and the explorations have a lot of buffs/debuffs/artifacts. Also the faction gimmicks are mostly complex, but because of the bad translation, you need to rely a lot on the trial and error method to learn. 

Overall a very satisfying experience if you enjoy gatchas, dark themed historys, complex gameplays but also can ignore a very poolry done translation.
